  "title": "Iconic Tooltips",
  "description": "Adds colors and icons to the tooltips of every item in the game!",
  "body": "![Iconic Tooltips](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/3e20128c355036ad91c8b9f62eebb047d776984c.png)\n#  \nAdds colors and icons to every item tooltip in the game with full language support!  \nIncludes all [Iconic Tooltips](https://modrinth.com/collection/wga7vVda) packs in one!  \n  \n![Example image](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4ba203d058dfd395fdd871971b3b4e6a2d6071e0.png)\n# \nIncludes tooltips for:\n- Armor Info\n- Armor Trims\n- Banner Patterns\n- Beehives\n- Bundle Descriptions\n- Command Execution Warning\n- Creative Categories\n- Crossbow Contents\n- Disabled in Peaceful Message\n- Durability\n- Dyed Leather Armor\n- Enchantments\n- Fireworks\n- Goat Horns\n- Maps\n- Music Discs\n- Paintings\n- Potions\n- Smithing Templates\n- Spawner Descriptions\n- Status Effects\n- Tool Info\n- Tropical Fish\n- Unused Item Components\n- Written Books\n#  \n_Inspired by, but not modified from [Enchant Icons](https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/enchant-icons-countxd)_",
